Event Handler di JQuery

================================

Contoh

Menggerakkan mouse di atas elemen
Memilih tombol radio
Mengklik elemen


========Menggerakkan mouse di atas elemen:=============

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Contoh Event Handler jQuery</title>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
      $("#myElement").mousemove(function() {
        alert("Mouse bergerak di atas elemen!");
      });
    });
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="myElement" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; background-color: gray;"></div>
</body>
</html>


==================Memilih tombol radio:==========================================


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Contoh Event Handler jQuery</title>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
      $("input[name='myRadio']").change(function() {
        var selectedValue = $("input[name='myRadio']:checked").val();
        alert("Tombol radio terpilih: " + selectedValue);
      });
    });
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <input type="radio" name="myRadio" value="Nilai 1"> Nilai 1<br>
  <input type="radio" name="myRadio" value="Nilai 2"> Nilai 2<br>
  <input type="radio" name="myRadio" value="Nilai 3"> Nilai 3<br>
</body>
</html>

=========================
